      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对世界两大经济体需求的担忧盖过了地缘政治风险加剧，油价跌至近六个月来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 23:31:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国页岩油生产商尽管承诺克制，但仍增加产量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/us-shale-producers-to-boost-output-despite-pledging-restraint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些美国领先的页岩油生产商计划今年的石油产量将超过最初的预期，这表明全国供应量可能超过许多公司承诺的温和增长预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/us-shale-producers-to-boost-output-despite-pledging-restraint</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 22:50:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：标普 500 指数或将迎来两年来最糟糕的就业形势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[疲软的就业报告引发人们担忧，美联储维持利率不变可能导致经济放缓更加明显，这导致股市抛售加剧，债券收益率暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 22:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
